name: Tydirium (V)
Lore: 'Stolen Imperial Lambda-class shuttle. Supposedly carried parts and technical crew. Delivered General Solo''s crack team of Rebel scouts to the forest moon of Endor.',
Text: 'May deploy (with a pilot) without presence or Force icons. May add 2 pilots and 6 passengers. May forfeit a scout aboard to cancel all remaining battle damage against you.',
